    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？　元気がないようだが\n新しいユニットがうまくいっていないのか？",
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ユニットは順調なんですけど\n私が大人っぽくなるのがうまくいかなくて……",
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ諦めてなかったのか……）",
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "最近は寮でもたまにスリクスさんの真似をして\n大人っぽく振る舞ってるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 22.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それを見たみんなから「大丈夫？　悩みがあるなら\n相談に乗るよ」って心配されちゃって……",
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "誰も私が大人っぽくなったと思ってくれないんです\nどうしたら大人っぽくなれるんだろう……",
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はどうしてそんなに大人っぽくなりたいんだ？",
      "startTime": 40.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "それは……子供っぽいって言われると\nなんだか成長してないって言われてるみたいで……",
      "startTime": 48.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私だって少しは成長したつもりです。でもまだ足りない\n私はもっと変わりたい……先に進みたいんです",
      "startTime": 58.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、千紗が大人っぽくなりたいのは）\n（成長したいという思いの表れなのか……）",
      "startTime": 66.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗、後でオフィスに来てくれないか？\n見せたいものがあるんだ",
      "startTime": 73.5401161443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夕方",
      "startTime": 76.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それで……私に見せたいものってなんですか？",
      "startTime": 78.1666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "実は以前、ライブに来てくれたファンに\nアンケートをとったことがあるんだ",
      "startTime": 85.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのアイドルで誰のどういうところが好きか\n書いてもらったんだよ",
      "startTime": 91.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、そこにあるアンケート用紙の束には\n私のことが好きって書いてあるんですか？",
      "startTime": 97.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。千紗のどんなところを好きになったのか\nファンの声を読んでみてくれ",
      "startTime": 104.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 108.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、ええと……「千紗ちゃんが\nひたむきに頑張る姿を見て勇気をもらった」",
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "「引っ込み思案な自分を変えようと努力しているのが\n見ていて応援したくなる」",
      "startTime": 120.6860505603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "「一番大人しそうなのに誰よりも頑張ってるところが\n好き。成長を見守っていきたい」",
      "startTime": 127.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "分かるか？\nみんな、ありのままの頑張る千紗が好きなんだ",
      "startTime": 133.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "ありのままの私が好き……\n頑張る私を応援して、成長を見守ってくれてる……",
      "startTime": 140.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "……私、不安だったんです。不器用で才能もなくて\n練習しても思うように上達出来なくて……",
      "startTime": 153.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "自分はちゃんと成長出来てるのか……\nちゃんと大人になれるのかいつも不安だったんです",
      "startTime": 160.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それでいいんですね。ありのままの私で……\n急いで大人にならなくてもいいんですね",
      "startTime": 169.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "無理して背伸びしなくていい。気負わずに自然体で\n自分のペースで大人になればいいんだ",
      "startTime": 176.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "……私、早く大人にならなきゃって焦っていたんですね",
      "startTime": 179.7666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "それが私らしくないって\n言われるまで気付かないなんて……",
      "startTime": 187.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "私より、いつも応援してくれてるファンのみんなの方が\n私のことを分かってるのかもしれませんね",
      "startTime": 195.682327548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n背伸びして大人っぽく振る舞うのはやめにします",
      "startTime": 201.1666920979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "悩みは晴れたみたいだな\n千紗らしい成長をこれからも楽しみにしているよ",
      "startTime": 207.6333587646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "startTime": 212.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10933.332316100006,
          "startTime": 223.3666656494
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、ライブに来てくれてありがとうございます\n一日だけの限定ユニット、最後まで楽しんで下さい",
      "startTime": 219.5333567302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（今日のライブは大盛況だ。千紗も年長者らしく）\n（落ち着いてパフォーマンス出来ているな）",
      "startTime": 228.1666900635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_02-chs022.m4a",
